item.title: CVE-2021-38334|2024-09-16T19:15:30.331Z -- wp%20design%20maps%20%26%20places -- wp%20design%20maps%20%26%20places
item.description: The WP Design Maps & Places WordPress plugin is vulnerable to Reflected Cross-Site Scripting via the filename parameter found in the ~/wpdmp-admin.php file which allows attackers to inject arbitrary web scripts, in versions up to and including 1.2.
